extractFrameworkClusterDepth

public static String extractFrameworkClusterDepth(org.neo4j.graphdb.Node frameworkCluster)
Extracts the depth of the framework cluster out of the cluster id which has the format 
[depth_in_tree]_[id]
.

Parameters:
frameworkCluster - the cluster node within the shared framework from which to extract the depth from.
Returns:
the depth of the given cluster or null if the given node is null, the node has not the desired cluster id property or the depth of the given cluster could not be extracted.

extractFrameworkClusterDepth

public static String extractFrameworkClusterDepth(String frameworkClusterId)
Extracts the depth of the framework cluster out of the cluster id which has the format 
[depth_in_tree]_[id]
.

Parameters:
frameworkClusterId - the framework cluster id from which to extract the depth from.
Returns:
the depth of the given framework cluster id or null if the given framework cluster id is null, is empty or the depth of the given cluster could not be extracted.
